&ldquo;We need to re-image your laptop&rdquo; &ldquo;Time to nuke and repave&rdquo; &ldquo;Your machine is totally borked&rdquo;
No one wants to hear those words come from IT. Especially developers. I&rsquo;ve had to deliver this news more times than I can count from users destroying their own machines either from messing with permissions, malware, or just from updates gone wrong.
I&rsquo;ve done my best to help alleviate some of this pain from the dev crowd by assisting in automating their environment setup on a net-new machine.
